frames.caption: A knight in golden armor rides a dragon through a volcanic landscape. The volcano in the background is actively erupting, with lava flowing down its sides and smoke billowing into the sky. The scene is set against a dramatic, fiery sunset.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantasy setting where a knight is mounted on a dragon, flying in front of an erupting volcano. The environment is vibrant and intense, with a focus on adventure and danger.

frames.caption: A majestic dragon soars through the sky, its wings spread wide against a dramatic volcanic backdrop. The volcano erupts with glowing lava and smoke, creating a fiery and intense atmosphere. A rider clad in armor sits atop the dragon, commanding the scene with a sense of power and adventure.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantasy setting where a dragon with a rider is flying in front of an erupting volcano. The environment is filled with vibrant colors and dynamic elements, emphasizing a sense of adventure and danger.
